data.description: Huge price reduction! Owner says sell!!! Best price on a home with an in-ground pool on the southside of Corpus Christi! Hurry before this one is gone. Fabulous 4 bedroom, 2.5 bath brick home with a POOL situated in a desirable Southside neighborhood! This home offers a spacious floor plan with 2 living areas perfect for gathering and entertaining! Kitchen is equipped with stainless steel appliances, tiled backsplash, custom cabinetry, breakfast bar and plenty of counter and storage space! Large primary suite with plenty of room for all your furniture complete with dual vanities, walk in shower and spa style tub perfect for relaxation! Spacious secondary bedrooms are a plus! Step out back to this Texas backyard with a covered patio and POOL ready for memories to be made with loved ones! Just a short drive to NASCC, Texas A&M CC, hospitals, restaurants, great schools & only a few minutes to the beach! COME SEE IT TODAY!
